HALF_CLOSED_LOCAL - streams.StreamState
half-closed (local): A stream that is in the "half-closed (local)" state cannot be used for sending frames other than WINDOW_UPDATE, PRIORITY, and RST_STREAM.
HALF_CLOSED_REMOTE - streams.StreamState
half-closed (remote): A stream that is "half-closed (remote)" is no longer being used by the peer to send frames.
